# My Recipe — always-on

- Product scope: `docs/product/vision.md`
- Architecture: `docs/architecture/overview.md`
- Workflow: `docs/development/workflow.md`
- Steering map (what goes where): `docs/development/steering.md`
- Task procedures: `.cursor/skills/*/SKILL.md`
- Next.js 16: read `node_modules/next/dist/docs/` before unfamiliar APIs. `cookies()`/`headers()` are async. Use `proxy.ts`, not `middleware.ts`.
- New Supabase tables need RLS **and** `grant` for `anon`/`authenticated`.
- Do not commit secrets (`.env*` except `.env.example`).
- Keep diffs scoped; update `docs/` in the same PR when behavior or scope changes.
